# Supply Chain Optimization â€“ Data Analytics Project

This project is part of the Naanmudhalvan Phase 3 Data Analytics initiative. It focuses on improving supply chain efficiency using predictive analytics and optimization algorithms.

## Problem Statement
We aim to minimize delivery delays and operational costs by forecasting regional product demand and optimizing delivery routes based on traffic and fuel data.

## Key Features
- Forecasting demand using Prophet time-series model
- Dynamic route optimization using Genetic Algorithms
- Integration of weather and traffic data for better planning
- Interactive dashboards for insight visualization

## Tech Stack
- **Language:** Python
- **Tools:** Google Colab, Flask (for deployment)
- **Libraries:** pandas, numpy, matplotlib, seaborn, plotly, Prophet, OR-Tools

